*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZNIHAL_SUBROUTINE
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT ZNIHAL_SUBROUTINE.

DATA : st_makt TYPE makt.

PARAMETERS p_matnr TYPE matnr.

PERFORM makt.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form makt
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM makt .
SELECT * FROM makt INTO st_makt WHERE matnr EQ p_matnr.
  WRITE :/ st_makt-matnr, st_makt-spras, st_makt-maktx.

ENDSELECT.
ENDFORM.
